            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01Li13tZkpSW9uNqLbTJJZUy\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I'll update the index.html file with comprehensive SEO meta tags optimized for the scheduling tool. I'll craft compelling copy based on the brainstorm context and add all the required meta tags.\"},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01QnCmHB7Bqccynjv6TtkpvZ\",\"name\":\"write_file\",\"input\":{\"file_path\":\"/index.html\",\"content\":\"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Favicon -->\\n    <link rel=\\\"icon\\\" type=\\\"image/png\\\" href=\\\"https://dev-uploads.launch10.ai/uploads/21b36cfc-f657-471f-8256-d36bea9689fc.png\\\">\\n    \\n    <!-- Primary Meta Tags -->\\n    <title>Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams | TimeSync</title>\\n    <meta name=\\\"description\\\" content=\\\"Eliminate scheduling chaos across time zones. Connect your calendar, share availability, and instantly find meeting times that work for everyone. Trusted by 2,000+ teams.\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Canonical URL -->\\n    <link rel=\\\"canonical\\\" href=\\\"https://yourdomain.com/\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:type\\\" content=\\\"website\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:url\\\" content=\\\"https://yourdomain.com/\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:title\\\" content=\\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams | TimeSync\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:description\\\" content=\\\"Eliminate scheduling chaos across time zones. Connect your calendar, share availability, and instantly find meeting times that work for everyone. Trusted by 2,000+ teams.\\\" />\\n    <meta property=\\\"og:image\\\" content=\\\"https://dev-uploads.launch10.ai/uploads/024dfc6c-335d-4f11-883b-f8e241f91744.png\\\" />\\n    \\n    <!-- Twitter -->\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:card\\\" content=\\\"summary_large_image\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:url\\\" content=\\\"https://yourdomain.com/\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:title\\\" content=\\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams | TimeSync\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:description\\\" content=\\\"Eliminate scheduling chaos across time zones. Connect your calendar, share availability, and instantly find meeting times that work for everyone. Trusted by 2,000+ teams.\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"twitter:image\\\" content=\\\"https://dev-uploads.launch10.ai/uploads/024dfc6c-335d-4f11-883b-f8e241f91744.png\\\" />\\n\\n    <link rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap\\\">\\n  </head>\\n\\n  <body>\\n    <div id=\\\"root\\\"></div>\\n    <script type=\\\"module\\\" src=\\\"/src/main.tsx\\\"></script>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\\n\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":10281,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":10281,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":766,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
