            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01YGTCxdoHVsfgeyGN3DFmXC\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I've successfully optimized the index.html file with comprehensive SEO meta tags. Here's what I added:\\n\\n## SEO Optimizations Applied:\\n\\n### ✅ Basic SEO\\n- **Title**: \\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams | TimeSync\\\" (59 characters - under 60 limit)\\n- **Meta Description**: Compelling 150-character summary highlighting the core value proposition and social proof\\n\\n### ✅ Open Graph Tags (Facebook, LinkedIn)\\n- og:type, og:url, og:title, og:description\\n- og:image using the second image URL (absolute HTTPS URL)\\n\\n### ✅ Twitter Card Tags\\n- twitter:card set to \\\"summary_large_image\\\"\\n- twitter:title, twitter:description, twitter:image (all with absolute URLs)\\n\\n### ✅ Additional Elements\\n- **Canonical URL**: Added for SEO best practices\\n- **Favicon**: Updated to use the logo image (absolute HTTPS URL)\\n\\n### 📝 Copy Strategy\\nThe SEO copy emphasizes:\\n- **Pain point**: \\\"Eliminate scheduling chaos across time zones\\\"\\n- **Solution**: Quick, automated meeting coordination\\n- **Social proof**: \\\"Trusted by 2,000+ teams\\\"\\n- **Target audience**: Distributed teams and remote workers\\n\\n**Note**: The canonical URL and og:url are set to \\\"https://yourdomain.com/\\\" - you should replace this with your actual domain when deploying.\\n\\nSEO_OPTIMIZED\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":786,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":10281,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":786,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":337,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
